[13:50:06    43]  
[13:50:06    43] -- Migrate `case_insensitive_strcmp`: it is a non-exported implementation function using raw C-string pointers and pointer arithmetic. Its callers must validate/convert FFI-derived strings at their existing unsafe boundaries before using a safe byte-slice comparison helper.
