[13:54:30     4] - Resume the `printbuffer`/`update_offset` migration in `rust/src/cJSON.rs`. `update_offset` cannot become safe alone because `printbuffer.buffer` is raw and all print routines write through it. Design an owned `Vec<u8>` path plus a borrowed preallocated-output path, then migrate the related printing helpers together.
